metadata.name: Mi-Pay Group plc
metadata.description: Mi-Pay Group plc engages in assessing, managing, and mitigating fraud risks in the cardholder-not-present payment solutions market in the United Kingdom, Ireland, rest of Europe, and internationally. It provides an outsourced secure payment services platform for instant top up and digital content services primarily in the mobile sector. The company operates in two segments, Transaction Services Revenues and Professional Services Revenues. The Transaction Services Revenues segment processes payment transactions on behalf of clients. The Professional Services Revenues segment develops, hosts, and delivers platform and client solutions. Mi-Pay Group plc was founded in 2003 and is based in London, the United Kingdom.
